          "audioFile": "tengu_match_start_astro_tengu_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/tengu_match_start_astro_tengu_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "You know, my sister told me that when I get mad, I should take a deep breath and count to four.  It doesn\u2019t always work, but sometimes it does.",
          "duration": 9.198
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
